---
description: Campfire Commerce storefront — invariants and API guide
alwaysApply: true
---

This is a Campfire Commerce storefront template (React 18 + TS + Vite +
MUI). AGENTS.md at the repo root is the canonical guide: codebase map, the
`@campfirecommerce/store-client` API reference, checkout lifecycle, and env
vars. Read it before structural changes.

Invariants:

- Never compute or send prices from the client; the API reprices every
  checkout server-side from `variant_id` + `quantity`.
- Never add card forms or Stripe.js — payment is Stripe-hosted Checkout:
  `useCart().pay()` returns `{ url }` to redirect to.
- Keep `src/context/CartContext.tsx` and the `/thanks?token=` polling route
  intact (or port their logic when restructuring).
- Money is integer cents; format with `money(cents)` from `useStore()`.
- Store identity (name, logo, `primary_color`, about, support email) comes
  from `useStore().store.settings` — don't hardcode it.
- Keep checkout actions disabled while `store.checkout_enabled` is false.

Everything visual — layout, typography, theme, pages, animation — may be
changed freely.
